{"tid":1421533,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"情境題！咁樣幫唔幫 割唔割？","createTime":"2019-08-06T08:19:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T08:27:32.000Z","uid":197852,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4266f353b8d062e5fba07e96b389057c6df9a65d","tid":1421533,"uid":197852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:19:08.000Z","msg":"琴日發夢北角先頭部隊比兩個大陸口音既女人屌<br />\n如果當時有人出手打藍絲<br />\n在場手足會唔會幫拖<br />\n其他人割唔割<br />\n<br />\n有個哨牙大陸女人為咗得到隔離兩個外籍人士嘅認同感<br />\n不停指住示威者對住外國佬叫go away<br />\n淨係識得講gp away<br />\n<br />\n之後有個絲打比另一個女人激到除口罩<br />\n但下次唔好咁傻豬豬"},{"pid":"c6109c27f5a73f546503b5a8da9cb5de0ba8bde0","tid":1421533,"uid":197852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:19:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"aa8919fb3ff2950730e04e9f0afdc6d21b10fc2e","tid":1421533,"uid":197852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:19:53.000Z","msg":"2推"},{"pid":"9b7e08393fef65676036f50bb7e0af35c47f228e","tid":1421533,"uid":197852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:20:03.000Z","msg":"3推"},{"pid":"4e435d109f6ec8d106e147dcd8b4b339bc5e3aac","tid":1421533,"uid":197852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:20:13.000Z","msg":"4推"},{"pid":"f2c430bcb747b8fc30fb88e8a3f0af9beacca2e3","tid":1421533,"uid":197852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:20:23.000Z","msg":"5推"},{"pid":"cab5ee7f45ef4817568225ef8c4fbf8748ee6f46","tid":1421533,"uid":197852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:20:33.000Z","msg":"6推"},{"pid":"1e0e32c7a6cc0a6d909b0b402d942f908cd88148","tid":1421533,"uid":281401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:20:34.000Z","msg":"幫"},{"pid":"1f0c147cda8fc6c1ea39abe666330647ee63db93","tid":1421533,"uid":197852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:20:47.000Z","msg":"1推"},{"pid":"4bf1f749e23334dfaa8ab15b144efeef507bf44d","tid"